'''Linkin Park''' ni band [[Amerika]] ya ''rock'' ubundi kuva Agoura Hills , [[California]]. Iri tsinda ryashinzwe mu 1996, ryabanje rigizwe na Mike Shinoda , Dave Farrell , Joe Hahn , Brad Delson , Rob Bourdon na Mark Wakefield , aba nyuma bakaba amajwi akomeye. Muri uwo mwaka, itsinda ryatangiye imirimo yabo ya mbere ya muzika yigenga hanyuma nyuma yibyo bandika ibikoresho byabo byambere byitwa ''Xero.''; icyakora ntabwo batsinze cyane mugushakisha label yanditse kuko ntamuntu numwe wagaragaje ko ashishikajwe nakazi kabo, bigatuma Mark Wakefield yegura.  Bidatinze, Chester Bennington yinjiye muri iryo tsinda nk'umuririmbyi; Iri tsinda ryerekanye bwa mbere mu ikipe ya Los Angeles kandi rishyigikiwe na Jeff Blue, icyo gihe wari visi perezida wa Warner Bros. Records , bashoboye gusinyana na label mu 1999. Izina ry’iryo tsinda ni ikinamico ku magambo yerekeza kuri Lincoln. Parike muri Santa Monika . 

Mu 2000 itsinda ryasohoye alubumu yabo ya mbere ''Hybrid Theory'' ;  muri ibi havuyemo ingaragu " Gukurura ", " Papercut ", " Amaherezo " na " Intambwe imwe Yegeranye "; bibiri bya nyuma, yabonye icyemezo cya zahabu muri Ositaraliya. '' Hybrid Theory'' yageze ku mwanya wa kabiri kuri ''Billboard 200'' , yari iya karindwi nziza - kugurisha alubumu yo mu myaka ya 2000,  kandi yemejwe na disiki ya diyama muri Amerika na platine nyinshi mu Burayi. '' '' Mu kane kimwe mu album, " Mu iherezo " yageze mwanya wayo neza mu mwanya wa kabiri mu rutonde ''Billboard Hot 100'' kwibera muri ibyumweru mirongo itatu n'umunani.
